ContestInfo.Comment: Good Wx and accident free flying,for which we Thank God. One aircraft with impulse coupler failed had a delayed start. Fed Ex delivered on time, maintence assisted installation. KOLE ASG Airport support Group provided breakfast, lunch and dinners (for a minimul charge). Sponsors were: Aircraft Spruce,Hope Propeller,SkyTec Starters, Blackstone Oil analysis,David Clark Headsets, Gene Beggs Spins in the Pitts and chicken wings by Mamosas' restaurant. Video by amazing aerial video.com, with a contribution of a large panoramic view of all contest aircraft and pilots. Total of 13 contestants. Buffalo Channel briefly 2 reported the event in three newscasts with Amazing aerial video supplying videos.
